org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry.item

Interface Item

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Item>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractItem, DigitalInputItem, DigitalOutputItem, ServoItem, TalonItem

    public interface Item
extends Comparable<Item>
    An item that can be graphed. These are used as Set elements and implementing classes should implement an identity-based version of equals and hashCode. The abstract base class implementing Item implements Comparable by comparing the results returned by Item#deviceId().
